      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "WITHOUT A TRACE (1) is worth forgiving last start after finishing fifth (42.38) at The Gardens over 715m. The form from her last run is stacking up nicely. Has ability and looks hard to stop. AMRON TOY (2) is a last start placegetter in Special conditions race company, jumping from this box and finishing a 1.5 lengths second over 650m at Warrnambool. Has a very honest record from this same draw, including a win and two minors. This tougher but looks a leading chance again. MEPUNGA LARA (8) was strongly fancied on the back of a win two starts back but finished second last time (42.45) at this track. Didn't win last time but still ran one of the quickest times on the card. Bold showing expected. LIGHTNING QUICK (3) gave nothing else a chance most recently. Big chance on that form.",
